  "prompt": "How much money can I deposit in my account?",
  "response": "The specific amount of money you can deposit into your account depends on the policies of your bank or financial institution. Generally speaking, there are usually no limits on how much money you can deposit into your account. However, some banks might have limitations on the amount you can deposit in a single transaction, or they might require additional documentation for very large deposits. It is best to check with your bank to understand their specific rules and regulations regarding deposits.",
